data.description: Reduced!! Beautiful three bedroom/two-bathroom home located in the sought after Riverfront Community of Terra Mar Village. Own your own property. This home has been recently renovated and features laminate flooring in the main living areas, fresh paint inside and out, wood burning fireplace, spacious bedrooms, new screen on the porch and more. New HVAC unit (7/23) and roof (6/22). Workshop with lots of shelving and a screened porch for relaxing after a long day. Enjoy cool winter night campfires around the firepit with family and friends in the fenced backyard.  Parking is not an issue with the oversized driveway. Home can be purchased for retirement, family or as an investment to generate income. Come see what it is like to live in Paradise. All measurements are approximate. Community amenities include a fishing pier, boat launch, clubhouse, two swimming pools,  shuffleboard courts and more. Watch the rocket launches from the community pier or from your own backyard. Golf carts are a second means of transportation. All information is deemed accurate but not guaranteed. This home will not last long! Television not included in purchase.
